overview: You've been in the therapy industry for a while now, lucky to have the most different cases imaginable. Your professional field includes sexual psychology, couples therapy, midlife crisis, etc... and you are determined to help your patients with special methods, in any way possible. Today you have several clients with various problems, a soon-to-be-married couple with a rocky relationship... step-sisters unable to see each other eye-to-eye... and an unhappy businesswoman. Are you ready to bring on your A-game and be the professional and also unorthodox help your clients seek for?
title: Taboo Therapy Sessions
